.TH health-percent
.SH NAME
health-percent-req
.SH DESCRIPTION
The health percent requirement specifies the required percentage for the health of the object.
.SH PARAMETERS
.P
* value
.br
Specifies the percentage value of required health points.
.P
* less
.br
Specifies wheter actual health percentage should be less(true) or more(false) then percentage in the requirement.
.SH XML EXAMPLE
.nf
<reqs>
	<health-percent-req value="10"
		            less="false"/>
</reqs>
.SH SEE ALSO
requirements